                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Though you aren’t a Giant, you grew up among giants. Maybe you were an orphan taken in by a sympathetic family of stone giants who raised you as one of their own. Or perhaps you lived in a lost prehistoric pocket of the world, surrounded by giants and fearsome behemoths or hulking dinosaurs."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "p",
        "children": [
